search_results.title: Ramon Lobato
search_results.snippet: Ramon Lobato is an author, researcher, and scholar of cultural industries. The focus of his research is on video distribution networks.

search_results.title: The Journey - The Art of Ramon Shiloh
search_results.snippet: Ramon Shiloh is an award-winning author, illustrator, activist for Native youth, and multicultural Chef of Black, Filipino, Creek, and Cherokee descent.
